title: Estrous Cytology "The Track-by-day method for monitoring the rodent estrous cycle" (Figure 6, Raimondi et al. Current Protocols)
description: Vaginal cytology images from adult Sprague Dawley rats for estrous tracking using Track-by-Day method. Cells are stained with H&E and full smear was imaged at 4x (tiles stitched) on a Keyence BZX700 microscope. Two sets are included in this archive: single-field smear images for four rats (Figure 6a), and full-smear images corresponding to cohort of n=12 (Figure 6b, c). These images correspond to sample dataset in Figure 6b, c in "The Track-by-day method for monitoring the rodent estrous cycle" (Raimondi et al., Current Protocols).
